00:16:17,700 --> 00:16:19,070
Ngapain kamu berdiri di sini?

254
00:16:19,300 --> 00:16:21,850
Biar aku yang bawa, kamu duduk aja.

255
00:16:22,470 --> 00:16:23,760
Silakan.

256
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:33,160
Kenapa harus sok keren sih?

257
00:16:36,010 --> 00:16:37,570
Kopinya jadi.

258
00:16:37,930 --> 00:16:39,880
Ini Americano pertamaku.

259
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,000
Silakan dinikmati.

260
00:16:53,450 --> 00:16:54,630
Gimana rasanya?

261
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:57,500
Kalau aku pemilik kafe...

262
00:16:57,990 --> 00:16:59,540
pasti sudah aku pecat kamu duluan.

263
00:16:59,580 --> 00:17:01,450
Kenapa?

264
00:17:01,540 --> 00:17:04,520
- Seburuk itu? - Jangan sajikan kopi kayak gini lagi.

265
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,150
Kamu kejam banget.

266
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,960
Kalau tidak lihat sendiri,
aku takkan percaya.

267
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,930
Kamu bisa berteman sama P'Hill.

268
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:11,930
Kenapa?

269
00:17:11,970 --> 00:17:14,990
Kamu dan P'Hill beda banget.

270
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:17,390
Kamu harus belajar kelembutan dari P'Hill.

271
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:20,040
Lihat kan, dia perhatian banget.

272
00:17:20,820 --> 00:17:22,290
Kalian lagi ngapain sih?

273
00:17:23,860 --> 00:17:25,440
Dulu Hill marah karena Ter
memujiku,

274
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:27,720
sampe teriak-teriak. Sekarang kamu pula.

275
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:37,310
Ya sudahlah.

276
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:39,830
Kalau begitu...

277
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:41,540
Boleh aku pergi sekarang?

278
00:17:41,600 --> 00:17:42,950
Bikin satu gelas lagi.

279
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:43,860
Hah?

280
00:17:44,330 --> 00:17:46,750
Buat sampai rasanya pas!

281
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:53,100
Ngapain ngelamun, cepetan!

282
00:18:06,210 --> 00:18:07,280
Nih.

283
00:18:09,870 --> 00:18:11,200
Masih hambar.

284
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,820
Terlalu encer.

285
00:18:23,290 --> 00:18:24,320
Bikin lagi.

286
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:27,140
Apa sih, kamu belum cicipi.

287
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,920
Lihat warnanya aja ketahuan.

288
00:18:28,950 --> 00:18:32,830
Semua kopi warnanya mirip kok, mestinya...

289
00:18:36,390 --> 00:18:38,210
Mungkin ada sedikit beda.

290
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:02,490
Aku tetap gagal, sebanyak apapun dicoba.

291
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:13,740
Aromanya aja udah manis.

292
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,840
(Kamu bakal kena!)

293
00:19:48,770 --> 00:19:51,640
Coba yang ini, pasti enak

294
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:07,300
- Sekarang boleh pergi - Hei!

295
00:20:07,650 --> 00:20:08,840
Kenapa?

296
00:20:10,190 --> 00:20:12,020
Kenapa? Mau tetap di sini?

297
00:20:12,730 --> 00:20:14,050
Siapa juga yang mau bareng
tukang goda!

298
00:20:14,060 --> 00:20:15,220
Kedengaran, tahu!

299
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:18,610
Aku pulang aja, deh.

300
00:20:18,650 --> 00:20:21,620
Kamu nggak berhak
memarahi atau naikin bayaranku!

301
00:20:21,670 --> 00:20:22,920
Aku benar-benar pergi.

302
00:20:25,850 --> 00:20:27,140
Coba lagi.

303
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:29,900
Kalau sudah habis, pasti mau
bukakan aku kafe sendiri.

304
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,980
Harus dihabiskan!

305
00:20:58,630 --> 00:21:00,060
Kenapa manis banget?

306
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,510
- Lalu diambil - Hahaha!

307
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:15,560
Lalu bawa portafilter-nya, bilang ke aku...

308
00:21:17,560 --> 00:21:19,330
Portafilter.

309
00:21:19,360 --> 00:21:21,620
- Portafilter. - Pelafalanku aneh ya?

310
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,190
Letakkan di sini.

311
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:24,760
Aku kembali!

312
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:28,010
Hei, lama banget di luar.

313
00:21:29,150 --> 00:21:30,760
Jangan-jangan gajimu dipotong?

314
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:32,990
Eh, P'Thun...

315
00:21:33,010 --> 00:21:34,750
Tolong kasihin aku, dong!

316
00:21:34,810 --> 00:21:36,540
Memang pantes banget!

317
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:39,430
Sini, belajar bikin kopi sama aku.

318
00:21:39,770 --> 00:21:41,900
Bikin kopi? Ampun deh...

319
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:43,530
Sekarang aku mau istirahat.

320
00:21:43,970 --> 00:21:46,330
Ngomong-ngomong, North,
aku sudah bicara dengan sepupuku, Chen.

321
00:21:46,330 --> 00:21:48,610
Soal kerja paruh waktumu itu.

322
00:21:48,650 --> 00:21:50,290
Aku kasih kontaknya, ya?

323
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:51,460
Terima kasih, P'Thun.

324
00:21:51,580 --> 00:21:53,850
Kamu memang selalu baik.

325
00:21:54,570 --> 00:21:57,540
Tapi bisa kuat kerja malam tiap hari?

326
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,720
Menurutku, awal-awal mending aku

327
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:02,100
temenin kamu. Gimana menurutmu?

328
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:05,080
Nggak apa-apa kok.

329
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:06,140
Aku bisa ke sana sendiri.

330
00:22:06,170 --> 00:22:09,290
Tapi itu bar, tempat minum alkohol.

331
00:22:09,320 --> 00:22:13,440
Bukan klub malam, lebih ke tempat santai.

332
00:22:14,120 --> 00:22:17,800
Biar aku aja yang antar,
aku kenal bosnya, ya?

333
00:22:19,290 --> 00:22:20,480
Oke.

334
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:22,880
Aku akan hubungi bosnya.

335
00:22:22,890 --> 00:22:24,800
Kalau dia jawab, kuceritakan ke kamu.

336
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,720
Terima kasih, P'Thun.

337
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,610
Sama-sama.

338
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:44,080
Boleh kamu minum.

339
00:22:45,370 --> 00:22:46,700
Kan kamu yang bikin.

340
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,160
Oke.

341
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,840
Hari ini aku jemput kamu ya?

342
00:22:53,130 --> 00:22:55,160
Selesai kelas jam berapa?

343
00:22:55,260 --> 00:22:56,730
Jam empat sore.

344
00:22:57,900 --> 00:23:00,030
Jam tujuh malam harus kerja.

345
00:23:00,130 --> 00:23:02,890
Kita makan malam dulu sebelum berangkat.

346
00:23:02,950 --> 00:23:05,200
Oke, sampai ketemu.

347
00:23:08,450 --> 00:23:09,600
Siapa itu?

348
00:23:09,770 --> 00:23:11,590
Bikin kaget aja.

349
00:23:11,820 --> 00:23:12,970
Siapa sih itu?

350
00:23:13,820 --> 00:23:14,760
P'Thun.

351
00:23:14,820 --> 00:23:16,250
Semester tiga manajemen.

352
00:23:16,300 --> 00:23:18,610
Dia bos kafe tempat aku kerja.

353
00:23:19,170 --> 00:23:22,060
Hari ini dia antar aku ke kerjaan baru.

354
00:23:22,190 --> 00:23:24,220
Kenapa dia yang antar kamu?

355
00:23:24,420 --> 00:23:26,030
Bosnya itu saudara dia.

356
00:23:26,030 --> 00:23:28,020
Katanya beberapa kali awal, dia bakal antar.

357
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,430
Masa aku tolak?

358
00:23:31,080 --> 00:23:32,520
Terus pulangnya gimana?

359
00:23:32,590 --> 00:23:34,200
Nanti dijemput dia lagi?

360
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,490
Iya.

361
00:23:36,230 --> 00:23:38,380
Kayaknya sih begitu,
kalau nggak, aku pulang gimana?

362
00:23:38,410 --> 00:23:39,750
Hei, tunggu deh.

363
00:23:39,770 --> 00:23:41,280
Dia mau deketin kamu?

364
00:23:41,350 --> 00:23:43,010
Iya nggak sih?

365
00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:45,010
Tahun dua kedokteran

366
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:46,780
atau tahun tiga manajemen?

367
00:23:46,890 --> 00:23:48,080
Pilih yang mana, ya?

368
00:23:48,210 --> 00:23:50,510
Harus pilih yang di kedokteran!

369
00:23:50,530 --> 00:23:52,790
Aku suka banget pasangan ini!

370
00:23:52,850 --> 00:23:54,130
Aku nggak pilih siapa-siapa.

371
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:56,920
P'Johan bakal kecewa kalau dengar itu.

372
00:24:11,150 --> 00:24:13,960
Dia biasanya tak pernah izinkan kita pulang awal, hari ini luar biasa.

373
00:24:14,050 --> 00:24:14,790
Iya.

374
00:24:14,860 --> 00:24:16,780
Kalian mau ke mana nanti?

375
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:19,720
Mau makan siang? Aku lapar.

376
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:21,860
Boleh saja. North, bagaimana denganmu?

377
00:24:21,910 --> 00:24:24,030
Kalian saja, aku akan pergi sama P'Thun.

378
00:24:24,110 --> 00:24:25,360
Ah.

379
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:27,930
Pasti dia mau deketin kamu.

380
00:24:28,910 --> 00:24:31,690
Kalau kamu? Mau ikut sama kami dulu?

381
00:24:32,020 --> 00:24:34,080
Kalian saja, aku mau mampir ke klub.

382
00:24:34,100 --> 00:24:35,030
Sampai jumpa.

383
00:24:35,050 --> 00:24:36,490
Dia kenapa?

384
00:24:36,700 --> 00:24:38,100
Aku bikin dia marah ya?

385
00:24:38,250 --> 00:24:40,280
Nggak kok.

386
00:24:40,570 --> 00:24:41,750
Apaan sih?

387
00:24:41,850 --> 00:24:43,480
Itu naga? Seru banget kelihatannya.

388
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:45,870
Itu awan, langit. Lihat deh.

389
00:24:45,950 --> 00:24:48,040
- Langit di sana, jangan gerak! - Hei!

390
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:49,880
Menjauh!

391
00:24:49,950 --> 00:24:51,800
- Nanti catnya kena bajuku. - Kok nggak boleh aku sentuh?

392
00:24:51,850 --> 00:24:54,500
Dao, setiap hari gambar terus, nggak bosen?

393
00:24:55,350 --> 00:24:56,710
Nggak.

394
00:24:56,730 --> 00:24:59,150
Siapa juga main terus kayak kamu?

395
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:02,600
Pantas.

396
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:05,900
Kalau aku, pasti nggak kasih kamu lolos.

397
00:25:09,870 --> 00:25:10,950
Hei, teman-teman!

398
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:13,360
Makan bareng malam ini yuk!

399
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:15,440
- Oke banget. - Setuju, fix ya.

400
00:25:16,130 --> 00:25:17,040
Siap.

401
00:25:17,140 --> 00:25:18,580
Aku sudah punya janji.

402
00:25:20,450 --> 00:25:22,670
Sama siapa? P'Johan?

403
00:25:22,790 --> 00:25:24,670
Bukan, sama P'Thun.

404
00:25:25,810 --> 00:25:28,360
Dia mau anter aku kerja.

405
00:25:28,580 --> 00:25:30,350
Dia ngajak aku makan malam.

406
00:25:34,090 --> 00:25:36,320
Hei, minggir, aku mau duduk.

407
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:38,860
- Sana juga bisa duduk kok. - Banyak omong amat.

408
00:25:40,030 --> 00:25:41,710
Kamu rasa P'Thun suka sama kamu nggak?

409
00:25:42,530 --> 00:25:45,500
Mulai ngegosip lagi nih?

410
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:48,280
Apaan sih, aku cuma dukung Johan sama North kok.

411
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:51,200
Seriusan? Kamu nggak ngerasa?

412
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:56,110
Dia suka elus kepala kamu, matanya juga beda lho.

413
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,440
Ngaku deh.

414
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:02,860
Pasti kamu juga ngerasa kan.

415
00:26:03,170 --> 00:26:04,430
Dia suka kamu.

416
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:07,830
Iya.

417
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:11,580
Mending jangan dipikirin, nanti malah awkward.

418
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:17,320
Mungkin saja dia nggak berniat apa-apa.

419
00:26:17,360 --> 00:26:19,300
Kita sama-sama mikirin diri sendiri.

420
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:24,440
Jadi?

421
00:26:24,850 --> 00:26:27,930
Kalau dia beneran suka, gimana?

422
00:26:30,500 --> 00:26:32,070
Kita cuma temen deket kok.

423
00:26:33,410 --> 00:26:34,740
Berarti aku kudu dukung kamu sama John nih.

424
00:26:36,010 --> 00:26:37,230
Keren banget.

425
00:26:37,890 --> 00:26:39,410
Kenapa kamu bahagia banget sih?

426
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:42,420
Nggak apa-apa, aku cuma pikir kamu cocok sama P'Johan.

427
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:49,540
(North, kamu udah selesai kelas?)

428
00:27:02,560 --> 00:27:03,590
Jo.

429
00:27:03,710 --> 00:27:06,980
- Kerjaan udah kelar? - Iya, sebagian udah.

430
00:27:08,030 --> 00:27:08,990
Syukurlah.

431
00:27:09,010 --> 00:27:11,160
Sekarang jarang lihat kalian di kelas.

432
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:13,080
Hari ini dia muncul, luar biasa.

433
00:27:13,170 --> 00:27:15,080
Kalau senggang, aku di sini terus kok.

434
00:27:15,420 --> 00:27:17,880
Biasanya kamu selalu sibuk.

435
00:27:17,970 --> 00:27:19,260
Sering banget nyuruh Hill bantuin kamu.

436
00:27:19,260 --> 00:27:21,220
Atau aku yang minta kamu bantuin ya?

437
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:25,200
Aku tahu kamu nggak mau belajar.

438
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:28,360
Tapi sudah kuliah, harus tanggung jawab dong.

439
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:30,340
Mulai kayak ayah aja, ceramah mulu.

440
00:27:30,600 --> 00:27:31,930
Suka banget ngeluh ya.

441
00:27:32,300 --> 00:27:34,140
- Aku pergi dulu. - Hei.

442
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:35,680
Ke mana?

443
00:27:35,750 --> 00:27:37,670
Beli kopi.

444
00:27:44,330 --> 00:27:46,030
(Aku di depan, di taman roda gigi.)

445
00:27:46,230 --> 00:27:47,730
(Maaf, kamu nunggu lama ya.)

446
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:50,420
(Aku maunya aku yang nunggu, bukan kamu.)

447
00:27:50,610 --> 00:27:51,860
(Kenapa?)

448
00:27:53,320 --> 00:27:55,220
(Aku pengen selalu lebih cepat dari kamu.)

449
00:27:59,020 --> 00:28:01,110
(Bercanda, aku cuma nggak suka orang nungguin aku.)

450
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,730
(Sampai nanti.)

451
00:28:04,980 --> 00:28:06,160
(Oke.)

452
00:28:13,390 --> 00:28:14,960
(Kamu di mana?)

453
00:28:16,930 --> 00:28:18,170
(Di kampus.)

454
00:28:19,360 --> 00:28:21,010
(Traktir kopi dong, biar aku jemput.)

455
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:23,030
(Kopi apa?)

456
00:28:25,080 --> 00:28:27,310
(Aku lagi sibuk, tapi bisa beliin kok.)

457
00:28:28,260 --> 00:28:29,900
(Kenapa kamu sibuk?)

458
00:28:32,170 --> 00:28:33,730
(Udah, aku jemput kamu saja.)

459
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:36,120
(Lagi di jalan.)

460
00:28:36,150 --> 00:28:38,120
Dia memang nggak pernah mau dengar omongan orang ya?

461
00:28:47,450 --> 00:28:50,020
- Satu americano, tolong. - Baik.

462
00:28:50,090 --> 00:28:52,020
- Mohon tunggu sebentar. - Oke.

463
00:28:59,450 --> 00:29:01,650
(Maaf, P'Thun. Sepertinya aku nggak bisa datang.)

464
00:29:03,430 --> 00:29:05,200
(Kenapa? Aku udah mau nyampe.)

465
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:11,440
(Maaf, mendadak ada urusan penting.)

466
00:29:11,730 --> 00:29:13,710
(Mau aku antarkan ke bar nggak?)

467
00:29:16,710 --> 00:29:18,540
(Biar aku sendiri aja, maaf ya.)

468
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:21,460
(Kamu utang makan sama aku ya.)

469
00:29:28,530 --> 00:29:29,540
Maaf menunggu.

470
00:29:29,820 --> 00:29:31,020
Ini kopi Anda.

471
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:33,260
- Ini. - Makasih.

472
00:29:35,970 --> 00:29:37,610
Aku udah di depan pintu.

473
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:54,110
Ini kopimu.

474
00:30:26,090 --> 00:30:27,260
Makasih.

475
00:30:29,800 --> 00:30:31,550
Kamu mau ketemuan sama siapa?

476
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:35,480
P'Thun, kamu mungkin nggak kenal.

477
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:37,740
Nggak kenal.

478
00:30:38,010 --> 00:30:40,020
Mau pergi ke mana sama dia?

479
00:30:40,890 --> 00:30:42,080
Makan malam.

480
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:50,800
Dia bos di kafe tempat aku kerja.

481
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:52,880
Hari ini dia yang antar aku kerja.

482
00:30:54,090 --> 00:30:55,500
Kerja?

483
00:30:56,260 --> 00:30:57,340
Iya.

484
00:30:57,690 --> 00:30:59,340
Aku dapet kerja part-time baru.

485
00:30:59,620 --> 00:31:01,440
Bosnya di sana saudara dia.

486
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:02,880
Di mana tuh?

487
00:31:03,650 --> 00:31:05,060
SeoulOut.

488
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:07,830
Bar ya?

489
00:31:08,280 --> 00:31:10,250
Iya, kamu tahu tempat itu?

490
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:12,650
Hmm.

491
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:17,060
Kita ke mana?

492
00:31:31,390 --> 00:31:32,430
Turun.

493
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:38,500
Kita mau makan malam ya?

494
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:41,200
Kamu pengen makan malam kan?

495
00:31:51,130 --> 00:31:53,580
P'Hill sering ajak aku ke sini.

496
00:31:53,670 --> 00:31:55,580
Aku nggak tahu kamu juga sering ke sini.

497
00:31:56,610 --> 00:31:58,260
Hill biasanya pesenin apa buatmu?

