Kenapa pakai speaker phone?

747
00:47:19,120 --> 00:47:21,390
Karena aku mau tanya soal P'Johan buatmu.

748
00:47:23,470 --> 00:47:26,170
Iya, gimana? Seru nggak?

749
00:47:27,370 --> 00:47:28,720
Biasa aja.

750
00:47:28,820 --> 00:47:31,910
Orang yang ajak aku ke sini cemberut terus.

751
00:47:37,660 --> 00:47:39,930
Maksudmu P'Johan?

752
00:47:41,050 --> 00:47:42,120
Iya.

753
00:47:42,160 --> 00:47:43,550
Tapi nggak masalah.

754
00:47:44,100 --> 00:47:45,230
P'Hill

755
00:47:45,950 --> 00:47:48,620
Ada yang goda P'Johan nggak?

756
00:47:50,660 --> 00:47:52,110
Ada kok.

757
00:47:52,410 --> 00:47:54,110
Tapi semua udah aku usir.

758
00:47:55,470 --> 00:47:56,930
Kenapa nanya gitu?

759
00:47:57,060 --> 00:47:58,220
Oh.

760
00:47:59,170 --> 00:48:00,450
Nggak apa-apa.

761
00:48:01,130 --> 00:48:02,110
Hmm.

762
00:48:02,530 --> 00:48:05,370
Aku cuma nanya buat temanku.

763
00:48:08,120 --> 00:48:11,170
Oh, aku paham.

764
00:48:12,020 --> 00:48:14,690
Lagi apa, kok belum tidur?

765
00:48:14,790 --> 00:48:16,030
Sebentar lagi tidur.

766
00:48:19,490 --> 00:48:21,070
Terus North?

767
00:48:22,190 --> 00:48:26,100
Dia sama aku, kenapa?

768
00:48:26,130 --> 00:48:29,790
Nggak apa-apa, cuma penasaran aja.

769
00:48:34,590 --> 00:48:38,190
- Besok jam sembilan ada kuliah kan? - Iya.

770
00:48:38,560 --> 00:48:41,600
Aku jemput kamu besok. Tidur sekarang, ya.

771
00:48:42,980 --> 00:48:44,770
Oke, selamat malam.

772
00:48:44,920 --> 00:48:46,190
Selamat malam.

773
00:48:51,820 --> 00:48:54,570
Udah, sekarang kamu bisa tenang.

774
00:48:54,870 --> 00:48:57,160
Nggak ada yang bisa goda P'Johan.

775
00:48:57,370 --> 00:48:59,330
P'Hill bakal jaga-jaga kok.

776
00:48:59,430 --> 00:49:02,870
Kamu sekarang santai aja, nggak usah khawatir.

777
00:49:03,630 --> 00:49:05,990
Kapan aku khawatir sih?

778
00:49:06,270 --> 00:49:09,150
Rahasiamu rapat banget.

779
00:49:11,130 --> 00:49:13,370
Aku cuma bercanda kok.

780
00:49:19,040 --> 00:49:20,220
Ini.

781
00:49:20,540 --> 00:49:22,680
Makanya harus ngopi di kampus teknik?

782
00:49:25,520 --> 00:49:27,380
Dia bohongin kamu apa?

783
00:49:28,200 --> 00:49:29,970
Dia diam-diam ngambil kerja sambilan.

784
00:49:30,220 --> 00:49:31,970
Kok tahu dia bohong?

785
00:49:31,980 --> 00:49:32,750
Iya sih.

786
00:49:32,860 --> 00:49:35,000
Aku lewat situ pakai mobil.

787
00:49:36,790 --> 00:49:39,530
Atau sengaja mampir ke sana?

788
00:49:40,860 --> 00:49:41,930
Tunggu dulu.

789
00:49:42,150 --> 00:49:45,800
Kerja diam-diam sampai larut, perlu marah banget?

790
00:49:45,830 --> 00:49:47,360
Itu kan bar.

791
00:49:47,490 --> 00:49:50,380
Tapi dia kerja buat balikin uang kamu, kan?

792
00:49:50,420 --> 00:49:51,750
Iya, tapi...

793
00:49:52,690 --> 00:49:54,130
Kerja di bar terlalu bahaya.

794
00:49:54,250 --> 00:49:57,290
Makanya kamu suruh orang jagain dia ala preman?

795
00:49:57,300 --> 00:49:58,830
Kamu kebanyakan bicara, Hill.

796
00:50:04,930 --> 00:50:06,910
Kalian nggak ngerti.

797
00:50:10,180 --> 00:50:12,730
Ngomong peduli aja, susah banget ya?

798
00:50:13,890 --> 00:50:14,990
Iya juga sih.

799
00:50:15,010 --> 00:50:16,990
Kayaknya temanmu bakal kena masalah.

800
00:50:30,390 --> 00:50:32,090
Ke hutan, cepat!

801
00:50:32,130 --> 00:50:35,810
Sembunyi di dalam, mereka datang.

802
00:50:35,960 --> 00:50:38,880
Nah, nggak mau dengar, mereka datang. Keren!

803
00:50:40,110 --> 00:50:41,380
Keren, ayo sini!

804
00:50:41,420 --> 00:50:43,740
- Wow - North

805
00:50:43,750 --> 00:50:45,460
- Bro - Hmm

806
00:50:45,550 --> 00:50:46,980
Kamu lihat tadi?

807
00:50:52,660 --> 00:50:54,680
(Aku di depan asramamu, turun.)

808
00:50:54,690 --> 00:50:56,550
(Bukannya sudah dibilang jangan ke mana-mana?)

809
00:50:58,000 --> 00:50:59,740
Ter

810
00:51:17,480 --> 00:51:19,220
(Promo minggu depan)
Kamu mau ajak aku ke mana?

811
00:51:19,240 --> 00:51:21,220
Kamu tidur di sini.

812
00:51:25,760 --> 00:51:27,420
Kamu pakai punyaku saja.

813
00:51:27,470 --> 00:51:28,360
Protektif banget sih.

814
00:51:28,360 --> 00:51:29,550
Itu jaket calon pacar masa depanmu?

815
00:51:29,580 --> 00:51:30,470
Udah, jangan bahas lagi.

816
00:51:30,490 --> 00:51:31,840
Kenapa pilih yang ini?

817
00:51:31,870 --> 00:51:35,300
Dia tipe yang Jo suka banget.

818
00:51:35,890 --> 00:51:38,160
Ter, kamu sama sekali nggak tahu soal neneknya Hill?

819
00:51:38,910 --> 00:51:40,750
Soal kakek-nenek P'Hill itu...

820
00:51:40,780 --> 00:51:42,790
Bisa ceritain ke aku nggak?

